summary: The guide overview includes resources for personal growth and strategic planning with an emphasis on aligning personal strengths and weaknesses. It features a course on conducting a SWOT analysis to clarify a startup's position and to formulate a strategic ask for networking and resource acquisition.
excerpt: Aligning the Misaligned involves a journey of growth and strategic planning. Discovering personal strengths builds confidence and direction. Embracing weaknesses fosters resilience and self-awareness.
